ZH: 我们明天早上坐列车去北京。
EN: We will take a train to Beijing tomorrow morning.

ZH: 这列火车是直达上海的。
EN: This train goes directly to Shanghai.

ZH: 我在站台等待我的列车。
EN: I am waiting for my train on the platform.

ZH: 这辆列车有空调吗？
EN: Does this train have air conditioning?

ZH: 坐火车比坐飞机便宜。
EN: Taking a train is cheaper than taking a plane.

ZH: 我错过了末班列车。
EN: I missed the last train.

ZH: 乘客们纷纷走上列车。
EN: Passengers started boarding the train one after another.

ZH: 这列火车总是很准时。
EN: This train is always very punctual.

ZH: 他的列车刚刚离开车站。
EN: His train just left the station.

ZH: 这是一辆高速列车。
EN: This is a high-speed train.

ZH: 列车将在半小时内到达目的地。
EN: The train will arrive at the destination in half an hour.

ZH: 我的列车还需要等待两小时。
EN: My train won't depart for another two hours.

ZH: 他坐的列车被取消了。
EN: The train he was taking got canceled.

ZH: 列车上的座位都被占满了。
EN: All the seats on the train are taken.

ZH: 这趟列车的车箱很宽敞。
EN: The train cars on this trip are very spacious.

ZH: 那列火车晚点了一个小时。
EN: That train was delayed by an hour.

ZH: 我们将乘坐慢车而不是快车。
EN: We will take a slow train instead of a fast one.

ZH: 列车员帮助我找到我的座位。
EN: The train attendant helped me find my seat.

ZH: 他们正在修理那辆出故障的列车。
EN: They are currently fixing the train that broke down.

ZH: 列车穿过一片美丽的山脉。
EN: The train passes through a beautiful mountain range.
